        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The Zend Tool application provider does an excellent job of creating the index.php and .htaccess files for standard PHP installations.  Unfortunately, this default configuration is incompatible with suPHP, used by many hosts.\r\n\r\nThe suggestion is either incorporating this variant in the application provider or providing notes in the documentation on how to modify the .htaccess and index.php files."
